			BILL_SUM_WO_TAX - sum without tax(es)
			BILL_SUM_TAX - tax part
			BILL_SUM_WO_DISCOUNT
			BILL_SUM_TAX_WO_DISCOUNT
			BILL_SUM_WO_TAX_WO_DISCOUNT
